de.rwth.i2.attestor.markings

Class Marking

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.markings.Marking

  • public class Marking
extends Object
    A marking specifies a single variable that should traverse all unfolded HeapConfigurations according to a grammar together with a (sub)set of selectors that should additionally be marked.
    Author:
    Christoph
